Interface Queue

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Any, Array, Composite, Serializable
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AnyQueue, NodeSpecification

    public interface Queue
extends Array
    Interface for Queue composites. Such composites can operate as LIFOs or FIFOs.
